{
  "name": "Phantom Steed",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A Large, quasi-real, horselike creature (or similar at the DM's discretion) appears on the ground in an unoccupied space of your choice within range. You decide the creature's appearance, and it is equipped with a saddle, bit, and bridle. Any of the equipment created by the spell vanishes in a puff of smoke if it is carried more than 10 feet away from the steed.</p><p>For the duration, you or a creature you choose can ride the steed. The steed uses the <strong>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.actors.Actor.mqLPiQO9TIUF2jYe]{Phantom Steed} </strong>stat block, except it has a Speed of 100 feet and can travel 13 miles in an hour. When the spell ends, the steed gradually fades, giving the rider 1 minute to dismount. The spell ends early if the steed takes any damage.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
